data.event: In 2013, San Francisco topped first as the "Most Competitive Municipality in the Philippines" according to the National Competitiveness Council (NCC) from out of the 163 first-class municipalities covered by their index.

event.title: became the municipality that it is now

data.event: Before San Francisco became the municipality that it is now, it was part of the District of Gibong, which was then governed by the late Deputy Governor Francisco Cataylo.
